723192f-a.title: Manhattan: Sheriff Street - Delancey Street
723192f-a.text:
Sheriff Street, west side, south from Delancey, to and including Grand
Streets, showing P.S. No. 34 (prior to 1931), at the N.W. corner of Broome
Street. This school bears No. 106 of the latter street.
Juy 1, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
